Text:
I didn't think there were
this many in all the Fringes!

If I never see an antlion
again it will be too soon!
What did I do to deserve this?
This was supposed to be easy...

Can you tassste the revenge
on your lipsss, my sssisters!?

Our sssisters will
not be forgotten!

Thisss land is ours
to do as we please!

The rocksss will run
red with your blood!

I'll have your legs
for sssupper!

You can leave on your
tails...or on your backs!
Tell your sisters of this day!

Back to the village! We must
plan our next attack!
We will suffer you no longer!

We cannot allow
them below deck!

Get those blasted
fiends off my ship!
Underfoot! We'll get ye out o' there.
I do not aim with my eye...

How did they slip
past our forces!?
Get your umbrellas out, 'cause it's gonna rain fists!
Corpse scum! Brace yourselves for pain!
Feel the might of imperial weaponry!
Witness the power of the new Fist!
Don't go dying in there, now!

I thought I told you
to watch our rear!

I've never shied from
a challenge, and I'm not
about to start!

Contact zone compromised.
Eradication measures initiated.

Alert status acknowledged.
Initiating combat protocols.

We was ambushed.
Never had a chance...

You cannot hide from
the moonlight!
Be in awe of my hissatsu!

Behold the pinnacle of
magitek enhancement!
Must be...protected. The Ruby Sea...must be protected...
Abyss...open wide! Show them what it means to be afraid!
Leave my sister to me! See that the voidsent are banished!
Fear me... Revere me... Worship me...!

Anyone!? Is there anyone
who might lend me their sword?

The Resistance will hear of
your deeds here today, friend.
More to test my blade on...

I almost want them
to come again...

I should be glad to
leave this place...

And that's the end
of that chapter.

Next time, I'm
coming with you!

Ah, I was just about
to go and fetch you...

Once across, I'll be but a
bell from my destination.

You...won't tell anyone
of this, will you? Good.

Leave no fish stan─
Swimming! No fish swimming!

Initiating Ice Break Protocol...
Critical failure...
Critical failure...

There! On the horizon!
Are those...bears!?

Shovels, men! We need to
fill the latrines before this
happens again!

How are we to stand against
the Empire if we cannot best
a few bears!?

Guard the trenches
with your lives, men!

No spirit will dine on my
soul this day or any day!
Fish!? No one told me there would be fish!

They're crawling out of the
very rocks!

Why, oh why did I not heed
my father's warnings?

Mighty Rhalgr,
send me your fists!

Is anyone out there!?
C-C-Can anyone hear me!?

I want to share
all my love with you.

I'll do anything for you.
You know I don't mind.

No one can deny
this love I have inside.

I'll give it all to you─
my endless love!

Kill them, Yojimbo!
Kill them all! Hahahahaha!

This is the last of my savings.
Do not fail me, Yojimbo!
R-Right! Give me just a moment...

P-Please, have mercy!
This is all I have left...
No...I don't like this place at all.
There are others who need us!
No Ala Mhigan is to be spared!

Rhalgr watch over
and keep you!
I take no joy in this...
For the glory of the Flames!

Reckon I'll be seeing you
again, my featherless friend!

Stay alert. Some will
hide in plain sight.

Who knows what awaits
me!? Who knows!?
Hurry home, I must... But the eyes─they are everywhere!

How kind of you, Gyogun,
to fetch us a basket of fish!
To begin with, I want you to...

Monster! Abomination!
Death will be a mercy!
Pray forgive me my sins...for laying down with Your enemies...
Help me...to cleanse my soul of this taint...
You defy the only rightful god!
No shield will defend you from the spear of my conviction!

Let us settle this
once and for all!
You shall fall, as did your ally!

I will answer for my sins.
Will you for yours?

You of all people
should understand!

We did everything right,
everything that
was asked of us!
Do not let her gain the village!
I am of no ussse like thisss...

We are witnesss to ssstrength
worthy of sssong, sssisters!

You have sssaved our
village! Peace be with you.

I am no longer worthy of
the beassstmaid's ssscourge.

There is nothing
more we can do.
TO VICTORY─COME HELLS OR HIGH WATER!
You're no match for my lance!
This bodes ill... Everyone, retreat to a safe distance. Now!
It intends to attack, once more! Hurry─we must disarm it!

My sssisters shame me
with their weaknesss!
Oh, what a fool I am!

You have my word as a
warrior, never again will I
allow my blade from my
sight! Honest!
Let us put you to the proof.
Drive them off! I beg you!
Leave this lot to me. Help the wounded!

There's not a more beautiful
river in all the land...

This is why we fight.
This is worth dying for...

Up on yer feet, dogs!
We've some shells to crack!

Yer messin' with the wrong
crew, ye Red bastards!

Our rum! The bastards made
away with our bloody rum!
Back to the deep with ye!

We are here for your
treasures. Run...or stay.
It matters not. You all
will die here today.

Thank you, stranger...
My brothers should be here soon.

Thar! Thar blows the blighted
fiend what swallowed me
poor, sickly brother whole!

Searched, I have for ye nigh
seven summers and a moon.

Come, Yahiro! Come that
I may tear out yer heart
as you did mine!

Yahiro is no more. Me blood
might now rest in peace.

I'll be back, I swear it. I shall
not rest until Yahiro's
blood stains the Ruby red.
And that and that and that!
Oh ho! A most tasty morsel!

Skewer you, we shall!
Roast you, we shall!
Tumble a savage? You sick bastard...
If Castrum Abania's fallen, there's nothing to stop them from marching on the city...
All part of the viceroy's plan. Probably...
Sound the alarum! We need reinforcements!
...She did things with her tongue you wouldn't believe. I'll introduce you if you like.
